; Relation branch test with full 8-bit labels

LOADA 0xA5
LOADB 0xA5
RPC_COMPARE
BR_EQ gt_test
LOADA 0x00
HALT

gt_test:
LOADA 0xA5
LOADB 0x5A
RPC_COMPARE
BR_GT lt_test
LOADA 0x00
HALT

lt_test:
LOADA 0x33
LOADB 0x55
RPC_COMPARE
BR_LT success
LOADA 0x00
HALT

success:
LOADA 0xEE
LOADB 0x11
RPC_ADD
HALT
